    <item id="done" text="confirm">
      <info url="media/devices/voco full generic dimmed.png">
        <shorttext>
          <span class="headline">Update modifications</span>
          <p class="description">Take the vocomedia remote in your hand! Hold it like you do for controlling your set top box. Your modifications will be uploaded.
Please be patient as this might take some seconds. The process finishes with three beep tones.
            <!--<br/>	  
            You can use &lt;Back&gt; on the vocomedia remote control to leave the menu after the selection was saved.-->
